  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02190', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-102-b8d45639', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依消防法規定，有關其建築物管理權人應使用防焰標示之地毯、窗簾等，其防焰物品或其材料非附有防 焰標示，不得銷售，違反者處其銷售或設置人員罰鍰為何？', '["新臺幣三千元以上一萬五千元以下罰鍰", "新臺幣六千元以上三萬元以下罰鍰", "新臺幣一萬元以上三萬元以下罰鍰", "新臺幣二萬元以上十萬元以下罰鍰"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:23+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0a34ee03f2ae", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d13e51cedf0e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102070", "c": "902", "s": "0708", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "消防法規概要", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年專技驗船師引水人、第一次食品技師考試消防設備人員地政士專責報關人員保險人員考試", "original_question_number": 27, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02191', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-102-b8d45639', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依消防法規定，依各類場所消防安全設備設置標準設置之消防安全設備，其設計、監造應由消防設備師 為之；其裝置、檢修應由消防設備師或消防設備士為之。違反上述規定者，處罰為何？', '["處新臺幣一萬元以上三萬元以下罰鍰", "處新臺幣一萬元以上三萬元以下罰金", "處新臺幣一萬元以上五萬元以下罰鍰", "處新臺幣一萬元以上五萬元以下罰鍰，經處罰鍰後仍不改善者，得連續處罰"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:23+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0a34ee03f2ae", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d13e51cedf0e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102070", "c": "902", "s": "0708", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "消防法規概要", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年專技驗船師引水人、第一次食品技師考試消防設備人員地政士專責報關人員保險人員考試", "original_question_number": 28, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02192', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-102-b8d45639', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依消防法施行細則規定，某場所之自衛消防編組依法設有滅火班、通報班、避難引導班、安全防護班及 救護班，則其員工人數係指在幾人以上者？', '["10人", "20人", "40人", "50人"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:23+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0a34ee03f2ae", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d13e51cedf0e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102070", "c": "902", "s": "0708", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "消防法規概要", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年專技驗船師引水人、第一次食品技師考試消防設備人員地政士專責報關人員保險人員考試", "original_question_number": 29, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02193', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-102-b8d45639', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依消防法規定，依法未設置火警自動警報設備之老人福利機構場所，而應設置住宅用火災警報器者，若其 管理權人未依規定設置或維護時，於發生火災之處罰為何？', '["致人於死者，處三年以下有期徒刑，得併科新臺幣六千元以上三萬元以下罰金", "致人於死者，處一年以上七年以下有期徒刑，得併科新臺幣一百萬元以上五百萬元以下罰金", "致重傷者，處一年以上七年以下有期徒刑，得併科新臺幣五十萬元以上二百五十萬元以下罰金", "致重傷者，處六月以上有期徒刑，得併科新臺幣五十萬元以上二百五十萬元以下罰金"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:23+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0a34ee03f2ae", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d13e51cedf0e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102070", "c": "902", "s": "0708", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "消防法規概要", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年專技驗船師引水人、第一次食品技師考試消防設備人員地政士專責報關人員保險人員考試", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02194', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-102-b8d45639', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依防焰性能試驗基準規定，防焰物品或其材料之防焰性能應符合下列何種規定？①地毯等地坪舖設物類', '["厚纖維製品餘燃時間不得超過二十秒", "厚纖維製品碳化面積不得超過 三十公分", "地毯等地坪舖設物類碳化距離不得超過十公分", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:23+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0a34ee03f2ae", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d13e51cedf0e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102070", "c": "902", "s": "0708", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "消防法規概要", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年專技驗船師引水人、第一次食品技師考試消防設備人員地政士專責報關人員保險人員考試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02195', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-102-b8d45639', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依建築法規定，建築物室內裝修應遵守下列何種規定？①供公眾使用建築物之室內裝修應申請審查許可', '["裝修材料部分得免除建築技術規則之規定", "不得妨害或破壞防火避難設施、消防設備、防火區劃及 主要構造", "不得妨害或破壞保護民眾隱私權設施", ""]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:23+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0a34ee03f2ae", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d13e51cedf0e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102070", "c": "902", "s": "0708", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "消防法規概要", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年專技驗船師引水人、第一次食品技師考試消防設備人員地政士專責報關人員保險人員考試", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02196', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-102-b8d45639', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依公共危險物品及可燃性高壓氣體設置標準暨安全管理辦法規定，硫磺及黃磷分屬第幾類公共危險物 品？', '["第一類及第三類", "第二類及第三類", "第二類及第四類", "第三類及第五類"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:23+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0a34ee03f2ae", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d13e51cedf0e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102070", "c": "902", "s": "0708", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "消防法規概要", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年專技驗船師引水人、第一次食品技師考試消防設備人員地政士專責報關人員保險人員考試", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
